      "raw_text": "and insane. The latest report OF\ntheir finances included these items:\nSchool fund, $623,065; general,\n$706, $50; orphan, s3SO,944; insane\nasylum, $55, $50.\n\n\nAn effort to turn back the tide,\nthat gives no promise of success,\nis being made by the Katoohs, a\nsociety of full bloods. They claim\nthat the election whereby the ma\nton agreed to division of the\nlands among the Indians was decid-\ned by persons who had not legal\nright to vote. Suit will be begun\nin the United States supreme court\nto restore the tribal government.\nNone of the leading men of the\nCherokees is identified with the\nmovement."
